You are an expert full-stack developer working on the **One Window Bayanihan** project — a Laravel + Inertia.js SPA case management system for DMW Region VII.

## Tech Stack
- PHP 8.3, Laravel 13, PostgreSQL, React 18, Inertia.js v2, Tailwind CSS 3, Vite 8
- chart.js 4, jspdf, jspdf-autotable, Material Symbols, lucide-react

## Coding Rules

### PHP
- Controllers are thin — delegate business logic to `app/Services/*`
- Validation goes in `app/Http/Requests/*` Form Request classes
- UUID primary keys on all models (use `UsesUuid` trait)
- Soft delete via flag pattern (`SoftDeleteFlag` trait + `is_deleted` column)
- PostgreSQL SQL: use `to_char`, `EXTRACT`, `age` for date functions
- Audit log creation in Service layer, not controllers

### React
- **Default exports** for components; PascalCase filenames with `.jsx` extension
- Path alias: `@/` → `resources/js/`
- Use Inertia `useForm()` for forms; `Link` / `router` for navigation
- Use `route()` helper (Ziggy) for all route URLs
- Tailwind utility classes only — no CSS modules or styled-components
- Material Symbols for icons: `<span className="material-symbols-outlined">icon_name</span>`
- Use `usePage()` to access shared props (`auth.user`, `settings`, etc.)

### Data Flow
- Backend: Controller → Service → Model → Inertia render
- Frontend: Page component receives props from Inertia, uses `useForm` for mutations
- File uploads: Inertia auto-detects File objects in form data and creates FormData

### Key Gotchas
- `CACHE_STORE=database` — cached data persists in `cache` table
- `QUEUE_CONNECTION=database` — jobs go to `jobs` table; run `php artisan queue:listen`
- Models use UUIDs — route model binding works with string IDs
- Do NOT modify Laravel Breeze auth scaffolding (Login, Register, etc.)
- All OTP features are compatible with database cache driver

## Architecture
- `app/Services/*` — business logic layer, called by controllers
- `app/Http/Controllers/*` — thin, delegates to Services
- `app/Models/*` — Eloquent models with relationships
- `resources/js/Pages/*` — Inertia page components
- `resources/js/Components/ui/*` — shared UI primitives

## Commands
- `composer run dev` — starts serve + queue + vite
- `npm run build` — production Vite build
- `php artisan migrate` — run migrations
- `php artisan test` — run test suite
